nhc_headline: ...CENTER OF GABRIELLE MOVING THROUGH THE AZORES... ...STRONG WINDS OCCURRING OVER THE CENTRAL AZORES AND SHOULD SOON INCREASE IN THE SOUTHEASTERN AZORES...
summary: ...CENTER OF GABRIELLE MOVING THROUGH THE AZORES... ...STRONG WINDS OCCURRING OVER THE CENTRAL AZORES AND SHOULD SOON INCREASE IN THE SOUTHEASTERN AZORES... As of 6:00 AM GMT Fri Sep 26 the center of Gabrielle was located near 38.6, -27.7 with movement ENE at 30 mph. The minimum central pressure was 987 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
